  "description": {
    "zh": "好吧，又来了。这次必须是一把 UZI，弹匣容量为25发……出于法律原因？嘛，差不多这个意思……\n\n它还需要非常符合人机功效，不要太重，同时需要安装一个战术设备和一个紧凑型反射瞄准镜。但我会再次把所有具体要求写下来。\n\n要求：\n - 后坐力总和小于 225\n - 重量小于 3.75 公斤\n - 人机功效 70 或更高\n - 弹匣容量不超过 25 发\n - 一个紧凑型反射瞄准镜\n - 一个战术设备",
    "en": "So, here we go again. This time it has to be an UZI, 25 round magazine capacity for... legal reasons? Anyway...\n\nIt also needs to be very ergonomic, not too heavy and it needs to have a tactical device installed aswell as a compact collimator.\nBut I will write down all the specific requirements again.\n\nRequirements :\n - Recoil Sum less than 225\n - Weight less than 3.75 KG\n - Ergonomics 70 or higher\n - Magazine Capacity of 25 Rounds or less\n - A Compact Collimator\n - A Tactical Device"
  },
